      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there's no point anymore. everyone at school/work is just constantly talking about me and making fun of me behind my back. i cant even walk down the hall without feeling like everyone is laughing. it's like the whole world is just one big joke and i'm the only one who isn't in on it. i just want it all to stop.",
